{"about_the_game":"Soulfire is a souls-like, side scroller action competitive game, integrating (stitching) multiple game modes, including the classic battle royale mode. In the enhanced version of &quot;Weapon Master&quot;, you can choose your favorite type from a large number of cold weapons, and practice constantly to unlock its powerful abilities. In addition, you can also use a variety of secondary weapons, spells, and props to create a wealth of combat strategies. Whether it is melee, long-range, or support, there will always be a fighting style that suits you. May you survive to the end in the cruel dungeon fighting!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCompared to original Soulfire title, Weapon Master have the following noticeable changes:<br />\r\n1. Almost all of the game code have been rewritten. This resulted in much optimized performance, reduced lags and fewer frame drops.<br />\r\n2. All servers are listed together; you have the chance to fight with players all around the world!<br />\r\n3. Battle tempo is a little faster, but it is still under tweaking.<br />\r\n4. Other experimental modifications, such as camera control, which may have a greater impact on the gaming experience.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1657080/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1624445098","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1657080/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1624445098","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1657080/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1624445098","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1657080/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1624445098","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Soulfire is a soul